      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLYAWAY JACK (4) goes very well here starting seven times for three wins and three minors. Hit the frame latest (16.76) when third at this track in a Grade 5. Looks the one to beat with even luck. VENOMOUS MISS (8) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 16.72 beating Austrian Rose. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. One of the prime contenders. PANDA SNOW (3) latest effort finished 5th on May 18 over 300m at this track behind Divorce Papers beaten 5.5 lengths (17.03) in a Grade 5. Looks well placed here and among the chances. FORCE (2) scored last time and can measure up again.",
